{"tid":1308743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有感而發] 運動去向","createTime":"2019-07-12T03:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T05:52:13.000Z","uid":174950,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0fde1e1dd3f8c9b0fa5b22eee3229bd27a635a9d","tid":1308743,"uid":174950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:27:28.000Z","msg":"由612到而家，<br />\n好多人都話運動已經失焦。<br />\n由五大訴求到而家起連儂牆，<br />\n反紅媒等支線活動。<br />\n對我黎講，<br />\n每一個活動都有佢個意義，<br />\n亦有可能係致勝嘅關鍵。<br />\n<br />\n但係我發現有二個問題，<br />\n大家做緊支線都做到片體鱗傷。<br />\n咁又邊夠體力做主線任呢?<br />\n所以麻煩大家個連儂牆起還起，<br />\n唔好令到自己受傷。<br />\n既然大家都成日講Be water，<br />\n咁點解唔將連儂牆都做到Be Water呢?<br />\n見到有個巴打建議隨身帶住memo紙同水筆，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">周圍寫，周圍貼。</span></span><br />\n我覺得呢個建議唔錯，<br />\n大家都可以試下。<br />\n<br />\n另外就係主線任嘅問題，<br />\n自從上次71入左垃會，<br />\n就已經再冇主線做。<br />\n自己身邊都有好多朋友慢慢對件事淡左，<br />\n連我呀媽都問我件事係咪已經完左。<br />\n仲記唔記得我地有個loop?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">和埋非上街 -&gt; 設下死線 -&gt; 勇武派抗爭 -&gt; 和埋非上街</span></span><br />\n上面係我地主線嘅loop，<br />\n上次喺尖沙咀和埋非已經上街, 開左第三戰線<br />\n上水同沙田都係屬於第三戰線都要做，<br />\n所以上水沙田都可以做埋先。<br />\n但係我想問我地個deadline set左去邊?<br />\n係時候要重回主線打返政府同黑警啦各位。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要set返個deadline啦!!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山， 各有各做。<br />\n支線任，不受傷, 不流血。<br />\n五大訴求, 仲未回應<br />\nBe Water My Friend<br />\n香港人加油。"},{"pid":"282a6eed3d1a8e821de23d4da3251f6e8b746688","tid":1308743,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:28:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>聽日去上水 三個一齊推 </strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n[突發][713光復上水]一封北區居民寫給香港人的公開信<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1307753\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1307753</a><br />\n<br />\n！！緊 急 ！！突 發！！上 水 連 儂 牆 要 人！ ！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1308369\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1308369</a><br />\n<br />\n［抗爭支線］！七 月 十 三 ！光 復 上 水 ！踢 走 水 貨 客！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1307559\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1307559</a>"},{"pid":"be8bb5ef8785c1054a7a9fdcfced3f62602de54c","tid":1308743,"uid":174950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:41:03.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9b3e95023a86ea7f9b7e637a6f909d62a8de18c2","tid":1308743,"uid":5801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:41:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bce1ccd7f0a0f62e97a28478f2a8cdaceae6220","tid":1308743,"uid":174950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T05:31:59.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"24792465d44fcc929009feba8ed9067aeb473187","tid":1308743,"uid":174950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T05:52:13.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}